element.definition:
Patient ID in the center providing the information
mandatory

Gender of the patient
ConceptualDomain: FHIR:AdministrativeGender
mandatory

Ethnicity of the patient
ConceptualDomain: FHIR:Race
optional

Date of birth of the patient
mandatory

Date of death of the patient
optional

Center ID of the center providing the information
mandatory

Center ID of the center of origin of the patient
mandatory

Description of the cause of death of the patient 
ConceptualDomain: UMLS:C0007465
mandatory if DeathDate is set

Date of last news (= date of last patient visit if there is no other information available) (day is set to the 15th)
mandatory

Indicator of the patient's last known vital status (alive or deceased)
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:LastNewsStatus
mandatory

Consent for genetic analysis
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:Boolean
mandatory

International code for the related disease (other than cancer). 3 characters.
ConceptualDomain: ICD10
mandatory if ObjectClass is set

Date of diagnosis for the related disease.
mandatory if ObjectClass is set

Date of the end of the related disease (if occuring and known)
optional

International code for the localization of the oncologic primary site
ConceptualDomain: ICDO3:Topography
mandatory if ObjectClass is set

Family relationship
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:FamilyCancerHistoryParentage
mandatory if ObjectClass is set

The field 'Type' allows to describe the 'Cancer' event as a global disease, as well as the various events constituting this disease (primary tumor, local relapse, metastatic relapse...)
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:EventType
mandatory

Date of start of cancer event or disease
mandatory

Date of end of cancer event or disease
optional

Definition of the autonomy scale (Karnofsky scale or OMS)
ConceptualDomain: OMS:PerformanceStatus
optional

Tool for the evaluation of the general condition of the patient
optional

List of histological grading scales
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:HistologicalGradeType
optional, mandatory if HistologicalGradeValue is set

Value of histological grade
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:HistologicalGradeValue
optional, mandatory if HistologicalGradeType is set

List of stage scales
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:StadeType
optional, mandatory if StadeValue is set

Stage value
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:StadeValue
optional, mandatory if StadeType is set

Date of diagnosis of the tumor event
mandatory

Localisation of the primary tumor
ConceptualDomain: ICDO3:Topography
mandatory

International code of lesion / histological type / tumor morphology of the tumoral event
ConceptualDomain: ICDO3:Morphology
mandatory

Laterality of location (if it exists)
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:Laterality
optional

Size of the tumor, propagation the site of the primary tumor
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:T_TNM
optional, mandatory if either N, M or TNMType is set

Propagation at the ganglion level
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:N_TNM
optional, mandatory if either T, M or TNMType is set

Remote propagation, presence of metastases
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:M_TNM
optional, mandatory if either T, N or TNMType is set

TNM classification version
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:TNMVersion
optional

c, p, r,...
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:TNMType
optional, mandatory if either T, N or M is set

Type of analysis
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:AnalysisType
mandatory if ObjectClass is set

Date of analysis
mandatory if ObjectClass is set

Date of assessment of treatment response
mandatory if ObjectClass is set

Assessment of treatment response
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:RECIST
mandatory if ObjectClass is set

Biomarker name
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:BiomarkerCode
mandatory if ObjectClass is set

Biomarker value
mandatory if ObjectClass is set

Type of treatment
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:TreatmentType
mandatory if ObjectClass is set

CCAM code of the medical act
ConceptualDomain: CCAM
optional

Date of treatment start
mandatory if ObjectClass is set

Date of treatment end
mandatory if ObjectClass is set

Treatment performed in a clinical study setting
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:Boolean
optional

Name of the clinical study
optional, mandatory if ClinicalTrialContext is 'Yes'

NCT identifier of the clinical study
optional, mandatory if ClinicalTrialContext is 'Yes'

Quality of resection (anapath)
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:SurgeryResectionQuality
optional

International code of the adverse event occurring during treatment (excluding other cancer), only the first 4 letters.
ConceptualDomain: MedDRA_CTCAE-v5.0
mandatory if ObjectClass is set

Date of the diagnosis of the adverse event
mandatory if ObjectClass is set

End date of the adverse event (if known)
optional

Grade of the adverse event
mandatory if ObjectClass is set

Therapeutic classification code (5th level if possible)
ConceptualDomain: ATC
mandatory if ObjectClass is set

Name of the molecule
mandatory if ObjectClass is set

Unique identifier of the sample
mandatory if ObjectClass is set

Unique identifier of the parent sample (if there is one, example histo#)
optional

Date of sampling
mandatory if ObjectClass is set

Code of tumor localization
ConceptualDomain: ICDO3:Topography
mandatory if ObjectClass is set

Nature of the sample
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:SampleNature
mandatory if ObjectClass is set

Nature of the original sample (Healthy or Tumoral)
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:SampleOrigin
mandatory if ObjectClass is set

Mode of preservation
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:StorageTemperature
optional

Percentage of tumor cells quantified in the sample
optional

Protocol used for the experiment
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:TechnicalProtocol
mandatory

Technological platform name (provider followed by the platform name)
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:PlatformName
mandatory

GEO Identifier of the platform
optional

Date when the experiment was performed
optional

Name of the panel targeted by the experimental analysis (provider followed by the panel name)
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:PanelName
optional

Identifier of the pipeline used into the analysis (unique in the center)
mandatory

Calculated percentage of tumor cells in sample
optional

Calculated number of sets of chromosomes in a cell of the sample
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:AlgorithmicPloidy
optional

Calculated number of break points in genomic profile
optional

General type of the detected genetic alteration (high level type)
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:AlterationType
mandatory

Conclusion of the biologist on the pathogenicity of the variant before the Molecular Tumor Board
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:AlterationOnSample_Pathogenicity
optional

Conclusion of the clinicians wether the variant is actionable or not during the Molecular Tumor Board
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:AlterationOnSample_Actionability
optional

Is the ClinicalTumorBoardConclusion used to orient the treatment decision ?
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:Boolean
optional

Type of validation of the detected alteration
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:ValidationType
mandatory if ObjectClass is set

Validation method depending on the type of validation
mandatory if ObjectClass is set

Validation status of the detected alteration
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:ValidationStatus
mandatory if ObjectClass is set

Chromosome containing the genetic finding
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:Chromosome
mandatory

Nucleotide location for start of genomic finding on the positive (+) genomics strand, 1-based
mandatory

Nucleotide location for end of genomic finding on the positive (+) genomic strand, 1-based
mandatory

Genome Build used for reference
ConceptualDomain: FHIR:Sequence
mandatory

Type of the genome entity. For eg: gene, mRNA, ncRNA...
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:GenomeEntityType
mandatory

Database of the genome entity
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:GenomeEntityDatabase
mandatory

Identifier of the genome entity in the genome entity database
mandatory

Hugo gene symbol
mandatory if Gene

Type of the fusion event. For eg: translocation, readthrough
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:FusionType
optional

Position of the fusion point on the 5 prime partner
mandatory

Position of the fusion point on the 3 prime partner
mandatory

Specify whether the fusion is in frame
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:Boolean
optional

Number of reads pairs spanning the fusion
mandatory

Number of reads containing the fusion point
optional

Intensity of the measured signal
mandatory

Copy number status
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:SegmentGenomicStatus
mandatory

Is the segment located in a region of loss of heterozygosity ? (can be independant from copy number information
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:Boolean
optional

Plus strand reference allele at this position. Include the sequence deleted for a deletion, or '-' for an insertion.
mandatory

Plus strand observed alternative allele at this position. Include the sequence inserted for a insertion, or '-' for a deletion.
mandatory

Codified type of the DNA sequence variation
ConceptualDomain: LOINC:48019-4
mandatory

Reference Type
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:Annotation_ReferenceType
mandatory if DNASequenceVariation is set

Reference Database
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:Annotation_ReferenceDatabase
mandatory if DNASequenceVariation is set

Algorithm to predict the variation effect over the protein
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:MutationPredictionAlgorithm
optional

Prediction of the variation effect over the protein
optional

Level of confidence of the prediction of the variation effect over the protein
optional

Pfams domains related to alteration position
optional

Identifier of Pfams domains related to alteration position
optional

Human readable name for the region of interest related to the transcript (eg: exon1, intron1, UTR3')
optional

HGVS nomenclature on the chosen transcript
mandatory

HGVS nomenclature on the chosen protein transcript
optional

HGVS nomenclature on the given GenomeReferenceSequenceId.
optional

HGVS nomenclature on the given TranscriptReferenceSequenceId and experimentely observed on RNA.
optional

nomenclature of changes at protein-level
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:AminoAcidChangeType
optional

Prime end of the fusion partner
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:Annotation_FusionPrimeEnd
optional

Indicate wether the variant is on a splicing site
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:Boolean
optional

Total sequencing depth at the variant position observed in the specimen
mandatory

Sequencing depth of the alternative allele at the variant position observed in the specimen
mandatory

Indication of the existence of strand bias at the variant position
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:Boolean
optional

Genomic class of the variant (eg: germline, somatic, and prenatal)
ConceptualDomain: LOINC:LL378-1
mandatory

Level of allelic occurrence of a DNA Sequence Variation
ConceptualDomain: LOINC:LL381-5
optional

Type of the expression value corresponding to the level of data processing
ConceptualDomain: OSIRIS:ExpressionDataType
mandatory

Number of Study Related Series
ConceptualDomain: DICOM

Number of Series Related Instances
ConceptualDomain: DICOM
